docs.title: Introduction
docs.text:
I'm Jai Prakash, nice to meet you! 👋

🚀 Full-Stack Developer | 🤖 Generative AI Specialist | 📊 Data-Driven Innovator

docs.title: About Me
docs.text: With 6+ years of experience, I specialize in building robust, scalable applications that harness the power of Gen AI and data insights. My expertise lies in transforming complex ideas into impactful solutions.

docs.title: Key Strengths
docs.text:
• 💡 API & Backend Development: Skilled in Flask, FastAPI, and Django for high-performance APIs.
  • 📊 Data Visualization: Creating interactive dashboards with d3.js, JavaScript, and Bootstrap to make data actionable.
  • 💽 Database Management: Proficient with MySQL, PostgreSQL, and SQLite for seamless data handling.
  • 🤖 Generative AI & ML: Leading innovative PoCs in Generative AI and machine learning.
  • 🚢 Deployment & CI/CD: Streamlined deployments with Docker and GitLab CI/CD for efficient releases.

docs.title: Core Skills
docs.text: 🐍 Python | ⚙️ JavaScript | 🔗 RESTful APIs | 🤖 Gen AI | ☁️ Cloud (Azure) | 📈 Data Visualization | 🌐 Web Scraping | 🐋 Docker | 🔄 CI/CD
